<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Welcome' }) %>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>⚔️ Nations of Empire</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Build your nation. Forge alliances. Conquer the world.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-large btn-primary">Create Your Nation</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-large btn-secondary">Login</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-number"><%= nationCount %></span>
        <span class="stat-label">Nations</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-number"><%= allianceCount %></span>
        <span class="stat-label">Alliances</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-number"><%= warCount %></span>
        <span class="stat-label">Active Wars</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="features-grid">
  <div class="feature-card">
    <div class="feature-icon">🏙️</div>
    <h3>Build Cities</h3>
    <p>Develop your cities with infrastructure, industries, power plants, and commerce improvements to generate resources and revenue.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <div class="feature-icon">⚔️</div>
    <h3>Wage War</h3>
    <p>Declare war on rival nations. Launch ground attacks, airstrikes, naval battles, missile strikes, and nuclear weapons.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <div class="feature-icon">🤝</div>
    <h3>Form Alliances</h3>
    <p>Join or create alliances with other nations. Share resources through the alliance bank and coordinate strategies.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
    <h3>Trade Resources</h3>
    <p>Buy and sell resources on the global market. Post offers for food, coal, oil, steel, aluminum, and more.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <div class="feature-icon">🏛️</div>
    <h3>Govern Your Nation</h3>
    <p>Choose your government type, national policies, and war strategy to shape your nation's identity and bonuses.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-card">
    <div class="feature-icon">🏆</div>
    <h3>Climb the Rankings</h3>
    <p>Compete for the top spots in military strength, economic power, and overall nation score on the global leaderboard.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
